isis.stitle: TSI 97-12-08 - Performance Specifications for 1996 and 1997 Model Year DT 466 and the International® 530 Mechanical Type Engines Equipped with Injection Pump

subjectgroup.subject: Performance Specifications for 1996 and 1997 Model Year DT 466 and the International® 530 Mechanical Type Engines Equipped with Injection Pump

geninfo.para: Engine Performance Specifications are being released to service for the engine applications listed below.

note.para: Refer to the emission label on the engine to correctly identify the Engine Model Year and Horsepower Rating.
